<HEADLINE>
HOMERS 66 AND 66 ARE MINUTES APART 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: This is a late add to page 1.)  
(Eds: See also BBN-CARDS-EXPOS, BBN-METS-BRAVES, BBO-RHODEN-COLUMN,
BBN-VECSEY-COLUMN) 
(lh) 
 By MURRAY CHASS   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   In a remarkable bit of long-distance theater, Sammy Sosa and
Mark McGwire exchanged home runs 45 minutes apart Friday night,
