<P>
   HURRICANE GEORGES
</P>
<P>
   DOMINICAN-RECOVERY _ SANTO DOMINGO, Dominican Republic _ Several
days after Hurricane Georges pounded this island country leaving
hundreds dead and billions in damage, people are literally trying
to pick up the pieces of their lives. What's the mood of the
people? (Lipman, Cox News Service). ETA: 7:30 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   STORM (developing) _ The aftermath and cleanup, continued. What
were the worst-hit areas, and why? Power outages, water supply,
sanitation, etc. Damage estimates, power estimates. Panhandle now
gets set. (Moffett, Palm Beach Post) WITH PHOTOS AND MAP.
</P>
