   FBC-GATECH-UGA _ Georgia Tech ranks second to last in the ACC
for SAT scores. And for the biggest difference in scores between
football players and the student body as a whole, it ranks third
nationally. But Tech defends its program, as does Georgia, which
ranks in the middle of the SEC schools for SAT scores. (Fish,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30.
