<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Sunday,
XXXXX XX. If you have any questions, please call Kevin Catalano on
the Star's News Desk at (816) 234-4720.
</P>
<P>
   HEASTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ Economics column by JERRY HEASTER.
Story will move in the ``f'' category.
</P>
<P>
   MARCHING-RECORD (Kansas City, Mo.) _ A marching band marches to
set a record. By TIM BAXTER. Story will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
<P>
   PURPLE-HEART (Kansas City, Mo.) _ A Vietnam veteran receives his
Purple Heart, 28 years after earning it. By MATTHEW SCHOFIELD.
Story will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-09-26-98 2307EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
